danmaku.name: Wild mode
description: In Wild mode, anything can happen.
Test your skill against every pattern you can find in this game.

Border Sign「Boundary of Wave and Particle」
Border Sign「Boundary of Wave and Particle」- A
Border Sign「Boundary of Wave and Particle」- B
Rekindled「The Embers of Love」
description: Move with purpose or become trapped.

danmaku.name: Simple Danmaku for Cornering a Trapped Heart
description: You are forced to run around and desert me?
Can you dodge my inflation love?

danmaku.name: Sinister Spirits「Double Black Death Butterfly」
description: Heavy dodging, double rotation magic of major angle.

danmaku.name: Border Sign「Boundary of Wave and Particle」
description: Waves become particles, and then back to waves.

danmaku.name: Border Sign「Boundary of Wave and Particle」- A
description: Her two shikigami help her in the attack.
Dodging bullets coming from three directions will definitely be tough.

danmaku.name: Border Sign「Boundary of Wave and Particle」- B
description: Boundary of Wave and Particle and... uh... screen.

danmaku.name: Five Elements Sign「Philosopher's Stone」
description: The power of Fire, Water, Wood, Metal, and Earth combined.
This one-week magician is really giving it her all today.

danmaku.name: Q.E.D.「Ripples of 495 Years」
description: The pent-up frustrations of 495 years worth of imprisonment.

danmaku.name: Moriya shot
description: This's not a spell card, but it's an interesting attack.
Just like the Q.E.D, but the pattern is completely readable

danmaku.name: Native God「Froggy Braves the Elements」
description: A weaving spray of water in a rainstorm.
With all these trajectories, this attack could be a Fountain of Math.

danmaku.name: Scourge Sign「Mishaguji-sama」
description: A pattern from one of Suwako's outer world acquaintances.
The twisting pattern becomes more frantic as the festival closes.

danmaku.name: Crossroad Sign「Crossroads of Heaven」
description: Twelve paths to heaven make for chaos at the junction.
Aya is indeed the center of attention.

danmaku.name: Cork Sign「Mountain God Procession」
description: Intersecting walls of bullets join expanding rings of cork.
Stay away from where all three meet.
